OL,3,CAlstom plans new train services
OL,4,Cbetween London and Wrexham
OL,6,FNew train services between London, the
OL,7,FMidlands, Shropshire and North Wales
OL,8,Fhave been proposed.
OL,10,FTrain and rail infrastructure supplier
OL,11,FAlstom said its planned operation will
OL,12,Foffer passengers new direct links,
OL,13,Fquicker journeys and "more competitive
OL,14,Ffares".
OL,16,FServices are proposed to run between
OL,17,FLondon Euston and Wrexham up to five
OL,18,Ftimes per day in each direction from
OL,19,Fnext year.
