OL,3,CAlstom plans new train services
OL,4,Cbetween London and Wrexham
OL,6,FThey would call at Milton Keynes,
OL,7,FNuneaton, Coleshill Parkway, Walsall,
OL,8,FDarlaston, Wolverhampton, Telford
OL,9,FCentral, Shrewsbury and Gobowen.
OL,11,FAvanti West Coast is to withdraw its
OL,12,Fcurrent daily return service between
OL,13,FLondon Euston and Shrewsbury in June.
OL,15,FIt has been 13 years since train
OL,16,Fcompany Wrexham & Shropshire ` which
OL,17,Foperated between London Marylebone and
OL,18,FWrexham via Shrewsbury ` ceased
OL,19,Ftrading due to mounting losses.
