OL,3,CAlstom plans new train services
OL,4,Cbetween London and Wrexham
OL,6,FAlstom's proposed new operation is
OL,7,Fnamed Wrexham, Shropshire and Midlands
OL,8,FRailway (WSMR), and is being developed
OL,9,Fin partnership with consultancy SLC
OL,10,FRail.
OL,12,FAn application to run services will be
OL,13,Fsubmitted to regulator the Office of
OL,14,FRail and Road (ORR) on Thursday.
OL,16,FWSMR would operate on an open access
OL,17,Fbasis, meaning it would receive no
OL,18,Ftaxpayer-funded subsidies and take on
OL,19,Fall revenue risk.
