OL,3,CAlstom plans new train services
OL,4,Cbetween London and Wrexham
OL,6,FRail minister Hew Merriman said:
OL,7,F"These exciting proposals could see
OL,8,Fbetter connections for communities
OL,9,Facross North Wales and the Midlands,
OL,10,Fincluding direct services to London
OL,11,Ffrom Shrewsbury, Telford and Wrexham.
OL,13,F"Competition delivers choice for
OL,14,Fpassengers and drives up standards,
OL,15,Fwhich is why we continue to work with
OL,16,Findustry to help make the most of open
OL,17,Faccess rail."
