OL,3,CAlstom plans new train services
OL,4,Cbetween London and Wrexham
OL,6,FMost train operators in England are
OL,7,Fpaid a management fee, with the UK
OL,8,FGovernment holding responsibility for
OL,9,Fcosts and revenue.
OL,11,FScotRail and Transport for Wales Rail
OL,12,Fare under public ownership.
OL,14,FAlstom is the largest private rail
OL,15,Foperator in North America but if its
OL,16,FWSMR plans get the go ahead it will be
OL,17,Fthe first time it has run services in
OL,18,Fthe UK.
