OL,3,CAlstom plans new train services
OL,4,Cbetween London and Wrexham
OL,6,FThe company's managing director in the
OL,7,FUK and Ireland, Nick Crossfield, said:
OL,8,F"As the country's leading supplier of
OL,9,Frolling stock and train services, it
OL,10,Fmakes perfect sense that we now move
OL,11,Finto operating our own fleet to serve
OL,12,Fpassengers directly.
OL,14,F"Having been part of the fabric of UK
OL,15,Frail for two centuries, we're excited
OL,16,Fto enter this new era as an open
OL,17,Faccess operator."
