OL,3,CAlstom plans new train services
OL,4,Cbetween London and Wrexham
OL,6,FSLC Rail managing director Ian Walters
OL,7,Fsaid: "From the Welsh borders to the
OL,8,FMidlands, our routes will forge new
OL,9,Fconnections, linking overlooked
OL,10,Fregions of England and Wales with
OL,11,Fdirect services to and from London.
OL,13,F"Passengers will benefit from more
OL,14,Fcompetitive fares and new technology
OL,15,Fto simplify ticket purchasing for our
OL,16,Fnew services.
OL,18,F"Delighting the customer will be at
OL,19,Fthe forefront of what we do.
