OL,3,CAlstom plans new train services
OL,4,Cbetween London and Wrexham
OL,6,F"We want WSMR passengers to experience
OL,7,Fa new excellence in customer service
OL,8,Fonboard our intercity trains."
OL,10,FAndy Bagnall, chief executive of
OL,11,Findustry body Rail Partners, said:
OL,12,F"The evidence both here in Britain and
OL,13,Facross Europe shows that where more
OL,14,Fcommercial freedom exists for
OL,15,Foperators, it leads to better service,
OL,16,Fcheaper fares and greater efficiencies.
