OL,3,CAlstom plans new train services
OL,4,Cbetween London and Wrexham
OL,6,F"To deliver more benefits to
OL,7,Fpassengers, Government should make it
OL,8,Fa priority to remove barriers to open
OL,9,Faccess operations now and during the
OL,10,Fnext parliament, in parallel to wider
OL,11,Freform that harnesses private sector
OL,12,Foperators within a new public body."
OL,14,FLast week, the ORR approved an
OL,15,Fapplication by Grand Union Trains to
OL,16,Flaunch new services between London
OL,17,FEuston and the city of Stirling in
OL,18,Fcentral Scotland from June 2025,
OL,19,Fcalling at stations such as Milton
OL,20,FKeynes Central, Crewe and Preston.
